&lt;h4 id="cons-3"&gt;Cons:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Might generate inefficient or insecure code&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Requires careful review of generated code&lt;/li&gt;
