&lt;h3 id="example-use-cases-of-ai-tools-in-business"&gt;Example Use Cases of AI Tools in Business&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 id="case-1-salesforce-einstein-for-enhanced-sales-forecasting"&gt;Case 1: Salesforce Einstein for Enhanced Sales Forecasting&lt;/h4&gt;
